    "description": "MODIS/Aqua Sea Ice Extent Daily L3 Global 1km EASE-Grid Night (MYD29P1N) data set contains tiles of daily 1 km resolution nighttime ice surface temperatures and quality assessment data, gridded to the Equal Area Scalable Earth Grid (EASE-Grid).\n\nAs of August 2023, this data set is retired and no longer available for download. We recommend using <a href=\"https://nsidc.org/data/myd29p1n/versions/61\">MODIS/Aqua Sea Ice Extent Daily L3 Global 1km EASE-Grid Night, Version 61</a> as an alternative.",
